{"product_id":"henley-black","title":"HENLEY - BLACK","description":"\u003cp\u003eMODEL HEIGHT 5'9\" WEARING M SIZE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e220 GSM. Hefty Cotton Fabric. Slim Fit Body-Hugging Silhouette. 96% Cotton \u0026amp; 4% Spandex. Gender-Neutral. Made in India.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis premium 220 GSM slim-fit T-shirt is designed to elevate everyday essentials with a refined, body-hugging silhouette. Crafted from a luxurious blend of 96% cotton and 4% spandex, it offers the perfect balance of softness, stretch, and structure for all-day comfort. The hefty cotton fabric delivers a smooth, premium hand feel while maintaining breathability and shape retention. Thoughtfully made in India, this tee is built to move with you—enhancing your style with clean lines, superior fit, and lasting quality.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash inside out with similar colors using cold water. Do not bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to preserve fabric stretch and shape. Iron on low heat if required. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e220 GSM hefty cotton fabric for a premium, structured feel. Slim-fit, body-hugging design that enhances natural shape. 96% cotton and 4% spandex blend for softness, flexibility, and comfort. Breathable construction suitable for everyday wear. Excellent stretch and recovery for long-term shape retention. Made in India with a focus on quality craftsmanship.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47079282835610,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":47079282868378,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":47079282901146,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47079282933914,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currenc